data.enText: a Chinese method of treating pain and illness using special thin needles which are pushed into the skin in particular parts of the body

simple_means.memory_skill: acu 尖，锐利 + punct 点 + ure 表行为 → 用尖〔针〕点 → 针灸

tr: treatment of pain or disease by inserting the tips of needles at specific points on the skin

value.def: Acupuncture is the treatment of a person's illness or pain by sticking small needles into their body at certain places.

example.ex: All of those who received the true acupuncture experienced pain relief.
example.tran: 所有接受了针刺治疗的人都感到疼痛减轻了。

partsOfSpeech.dec: acu 尖 + punct 点；变尖 + ure 表行为 → 用针尖点 → 针灸
